<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">聽說古代文字中的<delay8 />聖書體<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是研究這座線索的雕塑，<delay8 />
才解讀出來的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一想到研究者的熱情，<delay8 />
我心裡也跟著激動起來呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">可以藉由衣服的飄動，
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感受到迎風而立的感覺～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是太出色了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這座英挺的雕塑<delay20 />是經過精心設計的。
從下往上看的時候，<delay8 />
最能體會到它的美～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">這就是傳說中的那幅有名的名畫。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那抹微笑真神秘啊～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這幅畫讓人感受到一陣不可思議的暖風～<10_4 />
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />該不會是這裡暖氣開得比較大<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />應該不是這樣吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這幅驚人的名畫最厲害的地方<delay20 />
就是它的動態感～<pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓我不禁想說一句<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「工作加油」呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在正中間的是公主，對吧！<delay frames="40" />
然後，左邊的是畫家<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />他在畫什麼呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果是在畫公主的話，
那就只能畫公主的背影了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
嗯～<delay20 /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這需要推理一下，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">原來美術<delay20 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不光是描繪美麗的事物。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看到這幅名貴的名畫，
我深深明白了這個道理，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這幅沉沒的名畫<delay20 />
明明是在描繪非常哀傷的一幕，<delay8 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我卻不禁覺得<delay20 />她美麗動人，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">雖然這幅神秘的名畫<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />氣氛有點可怕，<delay8 />
但我的目光卻總是移不開呢～
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還好<tag a="110" b="33" />
不是這種氣氛，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />仔細一看，<delay20 />這幅作品是用小圓點畫成的呢。<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我也很喜歡精細的工作，<delay8 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我大概做不到這種程度<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">這幅閃爍的名畫表現天空的方式<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />實在太棒了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我完全想不到可以這樣表現，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在這幅磅礡的名畫中的巨浪<delay8 />
真的氣勢十足！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以想出這種大膽的構圖，<delay20 />
作者的性格應該也滿大膽的吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這座武士的雕塑<delay8 />
看起來就像在守護這間展覽室呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是太可靠了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這座遠古的雕塑外型！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />整身的花紋！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還有<delay8 />絕對不能忽視的眼睛！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我不知道該不該這樣說，<delay8 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但實在是太可愛了～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是看到<delay8 />這座似曾相識的雕塑，<delay20 />
就會讓人不禁開始思考些什麼呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />這個是
<tag a="110" b="4" />捐贈的嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />竟然為了我們<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的很謝謝你！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>